thread.title_full: BRIEF-Enea Q3 operating profit increases to SEK 27.9 mln | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Enea Q3 operating profit increases to SEK 27.9 mln
text:
Oct 21 Enea AB :
* Q3 net sales 117.7 million Swedish crowns ($14.18 million) versus 105.0 million crowns year ago
* Q3 operating profit 27.9 million crowns versus 23.9 million crowns year ago
* "Our objective for full year 2015 remains to achieve revenue growth, and we expect earnings per share to improve compared to 2014"
